{
  "page": "Pono's khalasar",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Khal</i> <b>Pono's <i>khalasar</i></b> is one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasars</a></i> formed in the wake of <i>Khal</i> <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>'s incapacitation. It currently numbers thirty thousand riders.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Pono.27s_khalasar_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Pono's <i>khalasar</i> at the end of the third century</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pono%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pono%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Pono\" title=\"Pono\">Pono</a> is the first member of <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo%27s_khalasar\" title=\"Drogo&#39;s khalasar\">khalasar</a> to declare himself <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">khal</a></i> after Drogo's <a href=\"/index.php/Illness\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Illness\">illness</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pono%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> sets out with her <i><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daenerys_Targaryen%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen&#39;s khalasar (page does not exist)\">khalasar</a></i>, she is advised against going downriver by <a href=\"/index.php/Rakharo\" title=\"Rakharo\">Rakharo</a>. He says that is the direction that Pono went with ten thousand of Drogo's <i>khalasar</i>. Pono intends to sell thousands of <a href=\"/index.php/Slavery\" title=\"Slavery\">captives</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pono%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The <i>khalasar</i> of Khal Pono is reported to be near the headwaters of the <a href=\"/index.php/Selhoru\" title=\"Selhoru\">Selhoru</a>. His <i>khalasar</i> is said to be thirty thousand strong and other <i>khals</i> such as <a href=\"/index.php/Zekko\" title=\"Zekko\">Zekko</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Motho\" title=\"Motho\">Motho</a> fear Pono's <i>khalasar</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Pono's_khalasar_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Pono.27s_khalasar_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">Pono's <i>khalasar</i> at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pono%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Pono&#039;s khalasar at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Pono\" title=\"Pono\">Pono</a>, former <i><a href=\"/index.php/Ko\" title=\"Ko\">ko</a></i> in Drogo's khalasar, now Khal.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pono%27s_khalasar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_68\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 68\">Chapter 68</a>, Daenerys IX.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_12\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 12\">Chapter 12</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_8\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 8\">Chapter 8</a>, Tyrion III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP